Description: Rotenso Windmi Heat Pump Controller
 The Windmi Controller is a Modbus-based controller for the Rotenso
 Windmi air-source heat pump.  It provides a local web interface for
 monitoring and control, a structured logging system, and a demo mode
 for development without hardware.
 .
 Features:
  - Modbus TCP/RTU communication with the Windmi heat pump
  - Embedded web server with real-time status monitoring
  - Structured logging with configurable levels and file output
  - Demo mode with simulated device for offline development
  - Self-test for hardware register verification
  - Instance locking to prevent multiple instances
